ing: 4 cups mixed frozen vegetables, such as corn, carrots and green beans
des: "Add a little shallot and dried dill or tarragon to any mixture of frozen vegetables and have a delicious side dish on the table fast."
ins: Heat oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Add shallot and cook, stirring, until softened, about 1 minute. Stir in frozen vegetables. Cover and cook, stirring occasionally, until the vegetables are tender, 4 to 6 minutes. Stir in dill (or tarragon), salt and pepper.
